<li>I am so sorry for your loss.  Thinking of you and your family.</li>
<li>Words cannot express how saddened I am to hear of your loss.</li>
<li>Please accept my heartfelt sympathy during this difficult time.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and love as you grieve the loss of your [relationship to deceased].</li>
<li>Your family is in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
<li>May the memories of [deceased's name] bring you comfort.</li>
<li>I offer my sincerest condolences to you and your family.</li>
